divs: Sighting DetailsWhile looking on google earth in area 51 found a cave with 3 metalic objects coming out which look like saucers, I thought you would be interested in this photo. I also found alot of ufo's over Puru north of nazca. I also have had sightings in California and Colorado was camping on north coast California, was awakened by unknown factors and was awake as if I never was asleep. Tent was positioned facing east I looked north to see these 2 lights Flying south at a very slow rate. The one in front was bobbing up and down as if it couldn't be controled (line of flight looked like a heart beat line) the one in back was steady and streight. I watched this for some time until they were streight in my line of sight
